  <steps>
    <step order="1">Inventory all legacy references in `src/solutions/LegalWorkspace/src/`: grep for `sprk_todoflag`, `sprk_eventtodo`, `_sprk_regardingevent_value` (excluding non-todo paths), and any references to LegalWorkspace's local `CreateTodo` + `CreateWorkAssignment` components.</step>
    <step order="2">Refactor LegalWorkspace's local CreateTodo: replace with consumption of `CreateTodoWizard` from `@spaarke/ui-components`. Use the launch-context pre-fill prop (`initialRegarding`) per the contract doc from task 032 — wire the workspace context to pre-fill regarding (typically the workspace's matter or project).</step>
    <step order="3">Refactor LegalWorkspace's local CreateWorkAssignment: remove the `addTodo` flag + auto-create-todo feature per task 031's decision. Update the wizard to NOT write `sprk_todoflag` on the event.</step>
    <step order="4">Repoint `useTodoItems.ts`: change from `sprk_event?$filter=sprk_todoflag eq true` to `sprk_todos` filtered by the workspace context (the workspace's matter/project regarding lookup). Update the IEvent → ITodo type usage. Inline mapping from `sprk_todoid` to display fields uses the same shape as SmartTodo's ITodo (from task 020). Consider extracting an `ITodo` type from SmartTodo to a shared types location for reuse — OR redeclare locally in LegalWorkspace if duplication is acceptable for now.</step>
    <step order="5">Update `useTodoItems.ts` to consume the new FeedTodoSyncContext bus (task 023's `notifyTodoChange` + `subscribe(todoId, isActive)`) — refresh the todo list when a todo changes.</step>
    <step order="6">Update LegalWorkspace's SmartToDo widget component to render ITodo records (not IEvent with todoflag). Display fields per sprk_todo schema (sprk_name, sprk_priorityscore, sprk_duedate, statuscode).</step>
    <step order="7">Update LegalWorkspace's ActivityFeed if it directly renders todo entries from sprk_event todoflag (per audit). Repoint to sprk_todo or split feed rendering between events and todos.</step>
    <step order="8">Update any service-layer code (DataverseService.ts) that exposes legacy `toggleTodoFlag` or similar — either remove (preferred per OS-1) or repoint to a sprk_todo statuscode update.</step>
    <step order="9">Run `npm run build` in `src/solutions/LegalWorkspace/` — must succeed clean.</step>
    <step order="10">Run any existing tests in LegalWorkspace — pass.</step>
    <step order="11">Fluent v9 lint pass on changed files.</step>
    <step order="12">Repo grep `src/solutions/LegalWorkspace/src/` for `sprk_todoflag` and `sprk_eventtodo`. Confirm zero functional hits (JSDoc migration notes OK).</step>
    <step order="13">Verify the LegalWorkspace SmartToDo widget end-to-end (read-through trace): user clicks "Add To Do" → shared CreateTodoWizard opens with workspace context pre-filled as regarding → submits → sprk_todo created → FeedTodoSyncContext notifies → useTodoItems refreshes → widget re-renders.</step>
  </steps>

  <tools>
    <tool name="npm">Build + test</tool>
    <tool name="grep">Reference verification</tool>
  </tools>

