    <criterion testable="true">LegalWorkspace SmartToDo widget queries `sprk_todos` (not `sprk_event?$filter=sprk_todoflag eq true`).</criterion>
    <criterion testable="true">LegalWorkspace CreateTodo flow consumes shared CreateTodoWizard.</criterion>
    <criterion testable="true">LegalWorkspace CreateWorkAssignment no longer writes `sprk_todoflag`.</criterion>
    <criterion testable="true">Fluent v9 lint passes on changed files.</criterion>
    <criterion testable="true">Final schema cut readiness verified: ZERO `src/` references to `sprk_todoflag` outside `.claude/archive/` (or this project's own audit/spec/plan docs).</criterion>
